name: git recursive directories scripts
version: 1.0
author:  Miroslav Safr miroslav.safr@gmail.com
web: https://github.com/safrm/gr-scripts
description: let monkey work to be done by monkies :)

content: 
 gr-cleanall.sh ........... cleans up git clones in subdirectories
 gr-pullall.sh ............ pulls all and keeps local chanegs in  subdirectories 
 gr-pullresetall.sh ....... pulls all and resets local changes in subdirectories 
 gr-showall.sh ............ shows local tags versus current remote situation in subdirectories 
 gr-showlocal.sh .......... shows local tags and if it was edited in subdirectories 
 
 install.sh ........... executes installation to /urs/local/bin directory
